A suspected robber has been shot dead outside a mall in Westville in Durban, following a shootout with police. Image courtesy Rescue Care JOHANNESBURG - A suspect has been shot dead outside a mall in Westville in Durban, following a shootout with police. It's believed the shootout took place after an attempted robbery at a Pick 'n Pay and a Post Office. This is a developing. We will update it as and when new information is available.